file.name: me_front_spec.yaml
file.content:
openapi: 3.0.0
info:
  title: kearch meta search engine front API
  description: kearch meta search engine front API
  version: 0.1.0
servers:
  - url: '{scheme}://{me_host}:{port}/me/front'
    variables:
      scheme:
        enum:
          - http
          - https
        default: http
      me_host:
        default: me-front.kearch.svc.cluster.local
      port:
        default: '10080'
paths:
  /search:
    get:
      parameters:
        - in: query
          name: query
          schema:
            type: string
          required: true
        - in: query
          name: sp
          schema:
            type: string
      responses:
        '200':
          description: Search results.
          content:
            application/json:
              schema:
                type: array
                items:
                  $ref: '#/components/schemas/Document'
components:
  schemas:
    Document:
      properties:
        url:
          type: string
        title:
          type: string
        description:
          type: string
        score:
          type: number
